fields.request: Manual QA: Confirm TODO fixtures target the next patch
fields.request_details: Create a new TODO through the admin and leave the version blank. Verify it is saved for the next patch version (for example, 0.1.33 when the system version is 0.1.32 or 0.1.32+). Confirm the task appears in Release Manager Future Actions and the Pending TODOs report until it is completed.
